<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>smạḥ wlym, lḥn ạ̉jnby</author>
<hymn_number>93</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̉ʿṭny ạ̹ymạnaⁿạ fạ̉ry̱ mạ lạ yry̱ .. ynql jbạlaⁿạ ʿạlyẗ
 yry̱ ạlmstḥyl wqd ṣạr wạqʿaⁿạ .. rwḥ ạllh lyẓhr tẖmrk
 2- lyḥl slạmk fy qlby dạỷmaⁿạ .. ytẖbt fy wjh ạlʿạṣfẗ
 slạm yfwq kl ʿql sydy .. rwḥ ạllh lyẓhr tẖmrk
 3- ạmlạny ḥbaⁿạ wạsẖʿlny bnạrk .. ạ̉bqy̱ lyswʿ kẖạdmaⁿạ
 yfyḍ qlby lh bklạm ṣạlḥ .. rwḥ ạllh lyẓhr tẖmrk</lyrics>
<title>ạ̉ʿṭny ạ̹ymạnạaⁿ</title>
</song>